<h2>Wholesale pricing</h2>

<p>Wholesale rates apply at standing weekly volumes starting at <strong>1 lb per week per variety</strong> (about 16oz, or four standard restaurant clamshells). We price by volume, by variety, and by harvest stage. Message us with your weekly need and we'll quote.</p>

<h2>Delivery schedule</h2>

<p>We can match almost any kitchen's prep schedule. Our current routes hit Winter Park, College Park, Maitland, downtown Orlando, and the Seminole County suburbs. If you're in greater Orlando and we don't already drive past you, we'll build the stop in.</p>

